---
title: Double Portuguese-Style Prawns & Tomato Rice  with Peri-Peri Mayo & Parsley
description: Indulge your taste buds in a symphony of flavours with our Portuguese-style prawns and tomato rice. Succulent prawns, marinated in garlic and lemon, are expertly seared to perfection and presented atop a bed of fluffy, tomato-infused rice. Served with a dollop of peri peri mayo, this dish is an absolute delight!
